Uncertainty in forming a new government vs. financial results
Downwards trend last 30days but will increase again to 13.138
based on the open interest for Dec 15

Looking at the three-month trend, 13,000(ish) seems to have been established as a support level, even in the wake of the break down of parliamentary coalition talks last week. The DAX did spend some time above 13,200 from late October to early November but appears by and large to be bouncing between 13,000 and 13,200 lately.
